                <h1
                    class="md:text-5xl sm:text-3xl xs-text font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-800  dark:text-white "
                >
                    Front-End Developer
                </h1>
                <a
                 href="https://linkedin.com/in/joaquin-herrera-396150183"
                 target="_blank"
                 rel="noopener"
                 class="flex items-center transition md:justify-center md:hover:scale-105 xs-hidden"
                >
                    <Badge> Open to work</Badge>
                </a>
            </div>
            <p
                class="my-6 text-xl text-gray-800 dark:[&strong]:text-yellow-500 [&>strong]:font-semibold dark:text-gray-300 lg:w-full lg:text-left sm:text-center xs-center"
            >
                Hi, I'm Joaquin Herrera. A passionate Front-End Developer based in Buenos Aires, Argentinaüìç.
            </p>
            <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8 lg:justify-normal md:justify-center sm:justify-center xs-center">
                <SocialPill href="mailto:joaquin.xherrera1@gmail.com">
                    <Mail class="size-4"/>
                    Contact me
                </SocialPill>
                <SocialPill href="https://linkedin.com/in/joaquin-herrera-396150183">
                    <LinkedIn class="size-4"/>
                    LinkeIn
